{"tid":2406433,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[成日上大山飛車果班死仆街入一入嚟] 本地製作賽車遊戲100%還原大帽山荃錦公路","createTime":"2021-02-13T07:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T01:13:10.000Z","uid":121711,"like":204,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"7785018243d4c81937876d7c92b21d21400bd064","tid":2406433,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T07:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oUUamsMSaBSkE8XdE0KAdcU5c_g=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EW6C5VQ4XNHMPJUMNDO55TINOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoUUamsMSaBSkE8XdE0KAdcU5c_g%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEW6C5VQ4XNHMPJUMNDO55TINOI.jpg&h=b3de0601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港大帽山荃錦公路將於遊戲《Assetto Corsa》中成為遊戲賽道。<br />\n<br />\n《頭文字D》令賽車迷沉醉山路競速，日本有秋名山，香港則有大帽山！秋名山的賽道，大家應該在賽車遊戲中玩過很多次，而香港的大帽山賽道現在亦遊戲化，將於《Assetto Corsa》遊戲中免費玩到，一眾香港車手應該很期待吧！<br />\n<br />\n虛擬大帽山荃錦公路免費玩<br />\n賽車遊戲《Assetto Corsa》，將於2月14日起推出有「香港秋名山」之稱的大帽山荃錦公路賽道，<a href=\"http://玩家只需到賽道創作團隊網站plutonization.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E5%88%B0%E8%B3%BD%E9%81%93%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99plutonization.com&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=ad3ef582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">玩家只需到賽道創作團隊網站plutonization.com</a>，參照說明下載，便可於遊戲中免費一嚐大帽山實境模擬賽車的刺激爽快感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xHtS6CwLJzAc_pHJtxKTr3wa-Uw=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UAVQRIGEUFBQLO2NITHZH3NLLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxHtS6CwLJzAc_pHJtxKTr3wa-Uw%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUAVQRIGEUFBQLO2NITHZH3NLLA.jpg&h=89aa98c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Assetto Corsa》的大帽山賽道，由本地賽車及電競運動團隊Plutonization製作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sibwAf7DqsWA0gXUpCeuBUJBSTY=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T53A57VSHNEHLN4MFDIAOC3V5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsibwAf7DqsWA0gXUpCeuBUJBSTY%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT53A57VSHNEHLN4MFDIAOC3V5U.jpg&h=5eb10ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Assetto Corsa》的大帽山賽道，按照真實路段的地貌及環境製作，非常像真。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TZJGTpzjlm3saCEp9SGTdQcqujM=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YF3QGLGDMRBCRNDFZHNA4I5QRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTZJGTpzjlm3saCEp9SGTdQcqujM%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYF3QGLGDMRBCRNDFZHNA4I5QRA.jpg&h=ea80b63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2月14日起，玩家就可在《Assetto Corsa》遊戲中一嚐奔馳大帽山公路的滋味。<br />\n<br />\n這條實境模擬香港賽道，由Shell贊助本地賽車及電競運動團隊Plutonization製作，也是第一條100%還原香港實境的模擬山路賽道，團隊對照真實路段的地貌及環境製作，由實地考察至繪圖、調整等，花了近半年時間，絕對一絲不苟。《Assetto Corsa》的玩家將可透過遊戲感受模擬大帽山賽道上的馳騁滋味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4PlD53zDMy2cCqukpVhHH1B4Abk=/1048x705/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LPFR5KJAGZBDVACZPHUGJ2IFSI.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4PlD53zDMy2cCqukpVhHH1B4Abk%3D%2F1048x705%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLPFR5KJAGZBDVACZPHUGJ2IFSI.PNG&h=eab68614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賽車遊戲《Assetto Corsa》在Steam售$89，支援VR。<br />\n<br />\n參賽成為大帽山車神<br />\n由2月14日至3月6日，大家更可透過《Assetto Corsa》線上參與「 Shell虛擬山路競速大賽2021」選拔賽，玩家必須在遊戲中指定的Mini Cooper賽車參賽，期間玩家可以無限次挑戰，並會以最快速度完成賽道的成績作為計算進入決賽的資格。參賽者須先上網頁填寫報名表格完成參賽登記。排名最高的16名玩家會入選3月14日的決賽，並以一對一形式進行淘汰賽，冠亞季軍的挑戰者將可獲得Shell V-Power油券、MINI Lifestyle Coupon及 Lenovo電競專用電腦產品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/24uEcid0QTQfGbJeg7wo-pbQD38=/2500x1250/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4O5P26WDZRGSJJ3RIJNK77NISI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F24uEcid0QTQfGbJeg7wo-pbQD38%3D%2F2500x1250%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4O5P26WDZRGSJJ3RIJNK77NISI.jpg&h=b2ba5fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過《Assetto Corsa》遊戲參加比賽，成為大帽山車神，並有豐富獎品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210213/J3BIZBTSL5AQLNEVUXSN64GDNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210213%2FJ3BIZBTSL5AQLNEVUXSN64GDNY%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=6d41fa19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210213%2FJ3BIZBTSL5AQLNEVUXSN64GDNY%2F&h=a5254371\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210213/J3BIZBTSL5AQLNEVUXSN64GDNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">呢家打機都可以模擬飛大山啦，成日上大山飛車果班死仆街你地唔使再揸住架改到鬼五馬六嘅爛鳩H車上大山飛車，喺度累人累物，要飛就喺隻game入面飛飽佢啦，屌你老母!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"bfe06c0799a965262b028e880a5b8047e4c4da90","tid":2406433,"uid":330227,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔爭在還原埋新娘潭路<br />\n記住整埋啲神主牌 記念碑"},{"pid":"c0e91b26698c29fcee1fb6c49ecbec0808178ee0","tid":2406433,"uid":37107,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:50:04.000Z","msg":"屌真定假<i